msgstr "搜索和替换字符。"

#: Thunar.xml:1295(para)
msgid "Convert to uppercase, lowercase or camlcase."
msgstr "转换成大写、小写或混合。"

#: Thunar.xml:1298(para)
msgid ""
"Additional <emphasis>Bulk Renamers</emphasis> may be installed as plugins "
